If there is someone in the party who can use the

This isn't an ordinary key, it's sealed with
magic. There might be some kind of mechanism.

Hmm? Someone came to see me? I was bored, you
know. I'm glad you came!

Oh, it seems there's a friend of Harpy here. I'm
glad! I hope we can get along well!

This is my way of thanking you for helping me!
Thank you so much!
I'm glad it seems you're safe.

Hapi is super duper happy right now! I'm grateful
to you! I really like you! I'll stick with you!
I'm saved! Nice to meet you.
That's good. Nice to meet you.
\c[6]A new loli-mon has joined the party!

Ah, my glasses! I'm so relieved...! I knew I lost
them when we came to the hot springs. Thank you
very much!

Uwaaaan! The barking is so scary! But I can't just
run away!!!

Yatta na no! Thanks to Konoha, we were able to
repel the naughty woof-woof! With this, I'll
remember some super strong skills too, no!

It's scary, but let's include Hapi in the battle
party!
